reviewText: I took a class with Ken Nelson at Krapalu last year.  In the past month, I have found the practices really enhance my sleep and begin my day with more focus. I ordered the additional DVDs for a friend and cousin who are surviving and being treated for cancer.
Qigong & Taiji for Healing & Vitality: This cd was ok but honestly didn't give it much of a chance. Sorry but thank you.
